She made her movie debut in 1927, and retired from the silver screen in 1937 at the age of 20. She appeared in fourteen silent movies. Moran is known for her roles in No Babies Wanted and in Up the Ladder. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1917 births Category:2006 deaths Category:American silent movie actors
